---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-brand-teal/10 bg-brand-surface">
  <div
    class="mx-auto flex max-w-5xl flex-col gap-6 px-4 py-10 text-sm text-brand-teal/90 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between sm:px-6"
  >
    <div>
      <p class="font-bold text-brand-teal">NDMDs</p>
      <p class="mt-1 max-w-md">
        UMMSS-affiliated student society for neurodiverse and neurodivergent MD
        students at the University of Melbourne.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="font-semibold text-brand-teal">Acknowledgement</p>
      <p class="mt-1 max-w-sm">
        We acknowledge the Traditional Owners of the land on which the
        University of Melbourne stands, the Wurundjeri Woi Wurrung and Bunurong
        peoples of the Kulin Nation, and pay our respects to Elders past and
        present.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="border-t border-brand-teal/10 px-4 py-4 text-center text-xs text-brand-teal/70 sm:px-6"
  >
    <p>&copy; {year} NDMDs — Neurodiversity in Medicine Society</p>
  </div>
</footer>
